file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://test.lightapi.net
info:
  contact:
    name: Steve Hu
    url: www.networknt.com/example
    email: stevehu@gmail.com
  version: v1_0_0
  description: Test API
  title: TEST API
paths:
  /v1/address/{id}:
    get:
      description: Returns an address.
      operationId: getAddressById
      security:
        - test_auth:
            - api.r
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: id
          description: The address id
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
  /v2/address:
    get:
      description: Returns address list.
      operationId: getAddress
      security:
        - test_auth:
            - api.r
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
  /v1/contact:
    post:
      description: Update contact
      operationId: postContact
      security:
        - test_auth:
            - api.r
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
components:
  securitySchemes:
    test_auth:
      type: oauth2
      description: This API uses OAuth 2.0 with the client credential grant flow.
      flows:
        clientCredentials:
          tokenUrl: https://localhost:6882/token
          scopes:
            api.r: read information
            api.w: write information
